title: Tridadi Stadium
text: Tridadi Stadium is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Sleman">Sleman</a>, <a href="Indonesia">Indonesia</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is used as the home stadium for <a href="PSS%20Sleman">PSS Sleman</a> and <a href="Sleman%20United%20F.C.">Sleman United</a>. The stadium has a capacity of 12,000 people.
